text.section:
The application:
Shall be on the form that the Secretary requires;
Shall be signed and verified by the individual; and
Shall include:
The name of the applicant;
A statement that the applicant meets the requirements of this subtitle;
The location of the proposed hospice;
The name of the individual who is to be the medical director of the hospice care program; and
Any other information that the Secretary requires.
